# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [0.0.2] - 2022-08-09

- Constraining HomePage size for desktop screens.
- Google Fonts as assets, disabling network fetch.
- Support for localization, English and Portuguese.
- Style improvements, theme data primary and secondary colors.

## [0.0.1] - 2022-05-22
### Added
- Light and dark themes. An action button on home page app bar can switch between both.
- Custom widgets to display profile info on a padronized way.
- Contact info buttons for email, Github and LinkedIn.